data.title: Simple Rack and Stack | All Materials supplied | 2 hours onsite

description.html:
%description.html%


DRESS CODE: No denim; No athletic shoes; No hats or baseball caps; only collared shirts without business logos are allowed.

OVERVIEW

On this work order you are required to successfully complete the following:

  • Rack and stack server components
  • Connect all components via the supplied patch cables
  • Upload all required deliverables to this work order and enter your closing notes

EXPECTATIONS/REQUIREMENTS

  • Ensure timely arrival
  • Report to site with all listed required tools
  • Dress code - polo shirt, jeans and close-toed shoes
  • Covid safe PPE and work behavior expected onsite at all times

ONSITE INSTRUCTIONS

﻿%description.html%

  • Contact POC listed on work order upon arrival Phone Number is  877-573-4353 (ext-1)
  • Locate installation materials and take inventory before beginning work
  • Test ports for installation to ensure they are active
  • Install components and complete connections leaving a 10' service loop
  • Configure IP Addresses on each of the installed components
  • Work with NOC to ensure all installed components are visible and trouble shoot as necessary
  • Label each connection with label maker
  • Clean all packaging waste

ESCALATIONS

  • Equipment Hardware Issues: Wrong equipment shipped; Shipping Damage call Dave at 877-573-4353 
  • Equipment Access Issues: Incorrect I.P.; Incorrect Password call NOC and ask for Mark 877-573-4354
  • Site Access Issues:  Client not allowing access to servers, call James immediately at 877-573-4355 (DO NOT DISCUSS WITH END USER)
